    pytoml.core.TomlError: <string>(3, 1): msg

That toml:

    [table]
    key = 'val\ue'

Gives out this error:

    SyntaxError: (unicode error) 'unicodeescape' codec can't decode bytes in position 19-21: truncated \uXXXX escape

This toml:

    [table]
    key = '''value\n'''

Gives out:

    {'table': {'key': 'value\n'}}

But should give out (*by v0.4.0 specs*):

    {'table': {'key': 'value\\n'}}",{},{}
