1. Compile yang module attached in this report with pyang compiler.
2.
3.

What is the expected output? What do you see instead?
As per RFC 6020,
 The position value MUST be in the range 0 to 4294967295, and it MUST be unique within the bits type.
Hence compiler should throw error if we are providing value greater than maximum.
But I see no error.

