dshakya-mbp:BITS dshakya$



What version of the product are you using? On what operating system?
dshakya-mbp:BITS dshakya$ pyang --version
pyang 1.5

I am using on MAC OS (10.10.3 - Yosemite)


Yang code/file:

module turing-machine {

