2236,IssuesEvent,2017-05-27 15:54:24+00:00,84580587,rm-hull/OPi.GPIO,1915543,rm-hull,,,closed,Support for Pull up / Pull down resistors,"[{'id': 557872400, 'url': 'https://api.github.com/repos/rm-hull/OPi.GPIO/labels/enhancement', 'name': 'enhancement', 'color': '84b6eb', 'default': True}]",[],1,"It would be great (if not too complex) to add support for the RPi.GPIO `pull_up_down` argument of setup() since it is very common to have pull up/down set when reading an input. 
