3610,IssuesEvent,2017-05-23 08:09:58+00:00,29050338,mementum/backtrader,5713511,mementum,,,closed,Ichimoku: Not able to get line data with bar_shift>0 using resampled data,[],[],1,"After switching from Yahoo finance API (#311) I now use hourly data from [Tickstory](https://tickstory.com). 
To use the daily timeframe the data is getting resampled:

```

data = bt.feeds.GenericCSVData(dataname=path_to_history_csv,
