8484,IssuesEvent,2017-11-01 07:19:18+00:00,40713934,biolab/orange3-network,10597360,darjusp,555189,biolab,closed,[Question] Is it possible to create network from adjacency matrix?,[],[],5,"Hi, maybe such feature already exists within the package and i just haven't find it yet.
