9231,IssuesEvent,2015-02-27 18:37:47+00:00,9252533,numenta/nupic,15566,rhyolight,1039191,numenta,closed,Simplify docker setup,"[{'url': 'https://api.github.com/repos/numenta/nupic/labels/build', 'name': 'build', 'color': '006b75'}]",[],1,"I'm not aware of anyone using the CentOS variant of the Dockerfile (https://github.com/numenta/nupic/blob/master/docker/centos/Dockerfile).  In the interest of simplifying and reducing maintenance overhead, standardize on a single Dockerfile at the root.

