9409,IssuesEvent,2017-06-26 15:21:28+00:00,29798313,saltstack/salt-pylint,1018108,sixninetynine,1147473,saltstack,reopened,lookup for setuptools in sys.modules is a no-op,[],[],3,"Unless you import setuptools (which does not happen in `setup.py`), 'setuptools' will not be found in `sys.modules`, thus the lookup here:

