9437,IssuesEvent,2017-08-15 08:47:49+00:00,2665618,inveniosoftware/invenio,1698163,lnielsen,1157480,inveniosoftware,opened,scholar: subtitles not included in citation_title,"[{'id': 183096861, 'url': 'https://api.github.com/repos/inveniosoftware/invenio/labels/Branch:%20maint-1.2', 'name': 'Branch: maint-1.2', 'color': 'd4c5f9', 'default': False}, {'id': 96303764, 'url': 'https://api.github.com/repos/inveniosoftware/invenio/labels/Branch:%20master', 'name': 'Branch: master', 'color': 'd4c5f9', 'default': False}, {'id': 96237777, 'url': 'https://api.github.com/repos/inveniosoftware/invenio/labels/Type:%20bug', 'name': 'Type: bug', 'color': 'ff2a00', 'default': False}]",[],0,"(2) Subtitles are missing from titles included in the ``citation_title`` metatag, e.g. https://ddd.uab.cat/record/1296 includes:

```
<meta content=""Recollint valoracions de la natura"" name=""citation_title"" />
```
but the title in full is:
```
Recollint valoracions de la natura : perspectives ecològiques, econòmiques i culturals
```

https://ddd.uab.cat/record/164891 includes:

```
<meta content=""La sociología de la política educativa :"" name=""citation_title"" />
```

but the title should be:

```
La sociología de la política educativa : aportaciones al estudio de los procesos de cambio
```


http://doc.rero.ch/record/209977


```
<meta name=""citation_title"" content=""La Suisse, ou, Tableau historique, pittoresque et moral des cantons helvétiques"">
```

```
La Suisse, ou, Tableau historique, pittoresque et moral des cantons helvétiques : moeurs, usages, costumes, curiosités naturelles, etc.
```

http://doc.rero.ch/record/8488

```
<meta name=""citation_title"" content=""Grammatikunterricht: Alles für der [sic] Katz ?"">
```

```
Grammatikunterricht: Alles für der [sic] Katz ? : Untersuchungen zum Zweitsprachenerwerb Deutsch
```

For this issue, if the full title is not included in the ``citation_title`` tag, then citation-matching within the indexing system would not work well, and could cause citations to be missed (citations are a key component for indexing & ranking in search results).  ",{},{}
