**tea kettle/coffee pot** = to indicate the free beverages available to all patrons
**stove/oven/microwave** = to indicate the extent of the kitchen that is available for guests
**cat/dog/pets(both)** = to indicate that its cat friendly, dog friendly or pet friendly in general
**mountains/river/beach/ocean/volcano** = to indicate the type of views that the rooms provide
**hand-washing(*detergent bottle and scrub brush*)/machine washing(*washer or dryer*)** = to indicate the type of laundry service at the location
**hot shower/cold shower** = to indicate whether hot water is available
**free towel service/ towels for rent** = to indicate that towel come included or not
**garden(*flower box*)/ orchard(*fruit tree*)** = to indicate the diversity of the grounds at the location
**exercise activities: gym(*weights*), yoga (*downward facing dog or yoga mat*), pool (*swimming*), hiking (*backpacker with hiking stick*), canoeing, jet skiing, snorkeling etc**. = to indicate the type of exercise or recreational equipment available.

I havent attached a photo for each of these but I can provide further explanation as needed.",{},{}
