[..]
cat mcore_XXX/test_00000000.tx
[..]

Function call:
{fallback}() -> STOP 
return: ( ... garbage values ...)

### Expected behavior
STOP should return (0,0) (see http://solidity.readthedocs.io/en/develop/assembly.html)

### Actual behavior
STOP returns an array of random values
",{},{}
