11312,IssuesEvent,2017-04-19 18:19:47+00:00,16316451,GoogleCloudPlatform/google-cloud-python,4346,lukesneeringer,2810941,GoogleCloudPlatform,closed,Callback mechanism for listening to Pub/Sub messages,"[{'id': 139685153, 'url': 'https://api.github.com/repos/GoogleCloudPlatform/google-cloud-python/labels/api:%20pubsub', 'name': 'api: pubsub', 'color': 'cd7f32', 'default': False}, {'id': 77438582, 'url': 'https://api.github.com/repos/GoogleCloudPlatform/google-cloud-python/labels/type:%20enhancement', 'name': 'type: enhancement', 'color': '8bc34a', 'default': False}]",[],7,"I'd love for there to be a mechanism to set up perpetual pulling and acknowledging of Cloud Pub/Sub messages, the sort of thing that might enable code like this:

