12027,IssuesEvent,2017-07-13 21:37:23+00:00,49976939,learningequality/kolibri,25990164,laurenlichtman,3926525,learningequality,opened,"""Go to next item"" button changes from topic tree to recommended",[],[],0,"## Summary

