 - Operating system: Windows 10
 - Browser: Chrome

## Traceback or relevant snippet from server.log or browser console

```
INSERT TRACEBACK, LOG MESSAGES ETC. HERE
```

## How to reproduce

1. View channel bcd99d8aeef04ce6b9e25a88d87eedb7 and look at the Touchable Earth content in the ""social studies"" folder.
2. View video in first folder under Syria. View and finish video.
3. Click on ""go to next item"" and view the change on the top. 

