12098,IssuesEvent,2016-08-02 17:16:51+00:00,14991049,nccgroup/Scout2,18292736,HIMANSHU-ELIGIBLE,4067082,nccgroup,opened,Unrestricted traffic tagged when opening all ports for same security groups ,[],[],0,"https://github.com/nccgroup/Scout2/blob/master/rules/ec2-security-group-opens-all-ports-to-self.json#L8 tags the rule with ""Unrestricted Network Traffic within security group"" when all ports for TCP and UDP are open from instances in same security group. 

