12977,IssuesEvent,2017-11-29 01:01:28+00:00,63730598,ethereum/py-solc,205327,carver,6250754,ethereum,opened,Clarify solc unavailable message,[],[],0,"### What was wrong?

The error message is not clear, when solc isn't available.

