12979,IssuesEvent,2018-07-24 13:30:25+00:00,56251096,ethereum/web3.py,18537398,avatar-lavventura,6250754,ethereum,opened,eth_abi.exceptions.EncodingTypeError: Value of type <class 'str'> cannot be encoded by AddressEncoder,[],[],0,"* Version: 4.4.1
