13944,IssuesEvent,2017-11-30 15:24:49+00:00,33653601,jupyter/notebook,4519227,parmentelat,7388996,jupyter,opened,Changing the notebook metadata won't mark the notebooks as changed,[],[],0,"a very minor inconvenience, but after doing a change in the notebook metadata with *Edit -> Edit Notebook Metadata*, the notebook is not considered changed

