14274,IssuesEvent,2018-04-11 09:30:15+00:00,22685735,codecov/codecov-python,2041757,stevepeak,8226205,codecov,closed,Does codecov support multiple branches?,[],[],1,"If my repo does have a `.codecov.yml` file [like this](https://github.com/marlonbymendes/2018.1-Cardinals/commit/cd37bf83c737c324f7084910ed7d087d6c607118), configured for branch `codecov`, codecov.io/ shows code coverage only for the branch `codecov`, even if I commit on other branches.

