 If I add `queryset` in my `meta` then it work fine for both the Resource. But if i don't add `queryset` then it throws an error.

Here is the duplicate issue.  #1475 

The workaround is that i have added object_class=None in all my meta.

Is it a bug or Is it how it works?",{},{}
