16646,IssuesEvent,2018-01-28 04:59:40+00:00,43769764,graphql-python/graphql-core,1823405,Lucretiel,15002022,graphql-python,opened,Pass field names more accessibly to object resolvers,[],[],0,"Currently, if you want to look at the set of fields being requested by a child object in a resolver, you have to look deep in the AST, with an expression like this:

