> ValueError: operands could not be broadcast together with shapes (1,500) (2,) (1,500)

Do you know how to fix it?

My 2nd question was that while training the loss, binary_acc, val_loss and val_acc are always at 0. Is that normal?

I'm sure I messed at many part but I can't see where (I'm still learning about machine learning).
Thanks for any help you would be able to provide.

