17503,IssuesEvent,2016-11-16 19:38:24+00:00,26516210,certbot/certbot,6504915,bmw,17889013,certbot,closed,Support correct error namespace,"[{'id': 277074172, 'url': 'https://api.github.com/repos/certbot/certbot/labels/acme', 'name': 'acme', 'color': '888888', 'default': False}, {'id': 272789317, 'url': 'https://api.github.com/repos/certbot/certbot/labels/error%20handling', 'name': 'error handling', 'color': 'eb6420', 'default': False}, {'id': 281347824, 'url': 'https://api.github.com/repos/certbot/certbot/labels/has%20pr', 'name': 'has pr', 'color': '0052cc', 'default': False}]",[],5,"Currently Boulder uses the old 01-draft error namespace (`urn:acme:error:`) but we plan to move to the correct (as of draft-03) namespace `urn:ietf:params:acme:error:` in the near future. In order to easily transition it would probably make sense to support both namespaces for a short period of time.
",{},{}
